© Rick Bowmer, Pool/AP Photo Megan Huntsman, who is accused of killing six of her seven newborns and storing all of their bodies in her garage, appears in court Monday, Dec. 8, 2014, in Provo, Utah. Utah County Attorney Jeff Buhman says a plea agreement could be in the works for Huntsman, though it's too early to say what penalty his office will seek.
